floating-point operation bugs in qemu-alpha

When running the gnulib testsuite, I'm seeing test failures in the tests for libm functions
  cbrt
  cbrtf
  ceil
  ceilf
  coshf
  exp2
  exp2f
  floor
  floorf
  fma
  fmaf
